        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Oh Ye-Ji (Lim Soo-Hyang) is a ceramic artist. She dreams of finding ordinary happiness, but life throws her a twist when she falls in love with brothers Seo Hwan (Ji Soo) and Seo Jin (Ha Seok-Jin).\n\nSeo Hwan is an architectural designer. He falls in love with Oh Ye-Ji at first sight, but his feelings puts him up against his older brother Seo Jin. Older brother Seo Jin is a race car driver. He became attracted to Oh Ye-Ji after he met her for the first time at his father's workshop. Meanwhile, Carry Jung (Hwang Seung-Un) is Seo Jin’s ex-girlfriend. Even though they broke up, she can't get over him.",
            "source": "asianwiki",
            "source_link": "https://asianwiki.com/When_I_Was_The_Most_Beautiful"
